korean-ime-fixer (1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of Korean IME Fixer
  * Automatic Fcitx5 configuration for Ubuntu systems
  * GNOME Wayland session support via systemd environment.d
  * KDE Plasma Wayland support via plasma-workspace env scripts
  * X11 session support via profile.d scripts
  * Integration with Ubuntu's im-config system
  * Comprehensive Korean input support for browsers and applications
  * Complete package removal support

 -- Korean IME Community <maintainer@korean-ime.org>  Wed, 13 Aug 2025 14:10:00 +0900
